{"tid":1601283,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"金鐘灣仔銅鑼灣發夢心得","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:29:58.000Z","uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1b0d8a460c0d9efb3ea090e78fedee5c4b108f","tid":1601283,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"尋晚9.28 <br />\n<br />\n2028 15-20防暴係狗總出面天橋<br />\n同民陣講定2030會開始清場<br />\n2130開始搜巴士，搜電車<br />\n<br />\n-由於金鐘折返銅鑼灣既手足必經天橋，就嚇鳩手足話如果經過天橋會開槍，之後又手足走上山(往禮賓府方向)<br />\n<br />\n-速龍搭黨鐵去中環站準備圍捕<br />\n<br />\n-山上既路迂迴曲折，其實狗係封唔晒，曾經有3架豬籠係山上standby，所以大家要留意hkmaplive<br />\n<br />\n-狗車會由軒尼斯道同告示打道推進<br />\n<br />\n狗會停既Checkpoint(對我地危險)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣<br />\n1.世貿中心<br />\n2.時代廣場<br />\n3.SOGO<br />\n4.希慎<br />\n<br />\n金鐘<br />\n1.海富<br />\n2.膺君<br />\n<br />\n中環<br />\n1.碼頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88da99a8b003e76814e6d85b7981818e20d29b5","tid":1601283,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b802d30bad66508b19f6c697adc3e0f7e650179e","tid":1601283,"uid":225050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776f3e090b20eacab2e7f490e4cf1e1b3771cd5b","tid":1601283,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02747aee88ca79b5cad8a2a92c0cfc2a8f335118","tid":1601283,"uid":271289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim